# --- 防御设置页面 (核心精简指南) ---
msgid "🛠️ SBA 防御设置"
msgstr "🛠️ SBA Defense Settings"

msgid "📖 核心功能配置指南"
msgstr "📖 Core Configuration Guide"

msgid "1. <b>性能对账：</b>数据每 10 分钟写库。若觉延迟，按 <code>Ctrl + F5</code> 强制对账。白名单用户豁免所有拦截。"
msgstr "1. <b>Data Sync:</b> Every 10m. Press <code>Ctrl + F5</code> for instant sync. Whitelisted users bypass blocks."

msgid "2. <b>入口保护：</b>启用钥匙后，入口变为 <code>wp-login.php?gate=钥匙</code>。未携带参数将返回 403 阻断暴破。"
msgstr "2. <b>Gate Shield:</b> Access via <code>wp-login.php?gate=KEY</code>. Requests without KEY return 403."

msgid "3. <b>IP 信任：</b>看仪表盘 IP。若为 127.0.0.1 或内网 IP，请根据 CDN/代理环境切换至「Nginx」或「Cloudflare」。"
msgstr "3. <b>IP Source:</b> If Dashboard shows 127.0.0.1, switch to 'Nginx' or 'Cloudflare' source."

msgid "4. <b>AJAX 补丁：</b>无痕访问首页。若「访客轨迹」未增加记录，说明 PHP 被静态缓存截断，此时必须开启。"
msgstr "4. <b>AJAX Patch:</b> If Incognito visits aren't logged, your PHP is cached. You must enable this patch."

msgid "5. <b>爬虫防御：</b>「Cookie 校验」识别无状态脚本。内置「蜜罐陷阱」会自动诱捕并封禁扫描页面的恶意爬虫。"
msgstr "5. <b>Bot Defense:</b> Cookie check identifies scripts. Honeypots automatically trap and ban scanners."

msgid "✅ 信任通道"
msgstr "✅ Trusted Channels"

msgid "用户名白名单"
msgstr "User Whitelist"

msgid "登录此用户时，系统自动信任，不执行拦截逻辑。"
msgstr "System automatically trusts this user."

